						<h3 itemprop="name" class="not-hidden">
					Faye Shirekuli			</h3>
		<div itemprop="articleBody">
		<p>Ms. Faye Shirekuli, LL.B (Hons), Kampala International University. Dip. in Law (KSL), She is an Advocate of the High Court of Kenya and a member of the Law Society of Kenya. She is an Associate of the firm. She has specialized in Litigation in Civil and Criminal Matters, and Conveyancing and Commercial. She is a Kenyan National. She was admitted in the Roll of Advocates in 2016.</p> 	</div>

	
	
				
	
	
